


接口说明
=============
1. 以 `ip2city.http` 为例
2. zk集群名称说明::

    qa:  测试集群
    yz:  亦庄集群
    g1:  g1集群

3. 所有操作都是在 `/soa/services` 目录下


[接口]创建结点
-------------------
url: create/
参数::

    key:
    destName: 服务名
    zkHost: zk集群名(qa, yz, g1)

返回值:

    {code: <code>, reason: <reason>}
    1: 成功
    0: 失败

[接口]新增服务
-------------------
url: add/
参数::

    key:
    destName:
    zkHost:
    serverHost:
    serverPort:

返回值::

    {code: <code>, reason: <reason>}
    1: 成功
    0: 失败


[接口]删除服务(需慎重)
--------------------------
url: delete/
参数::

    key:
    destName:
    zkHost:

返回值::

    {code: <code>, reason: <reason>}
    1: 成功
    0: 失败

[接口]查看服务列表
------------------------
url: servicelist/
参数::

    key
    zkHost

返回值::

    {code:1, serverlist: [
        {service: <service>},
        {service: <service>}
    ]}


[接口]查看指定服务的机器列表
----------------------------------
url: get/
参数::

    key
    destName:
    zkHost:

返回值::

    0: 失败
    {code: 0, reason: <reason>}
    1: 成功
    {code:1, data: <data>}

举例说明::

    {"code": 0, "reason": "interal server error!"}

    {"code" : 1, "value" : [
       {"host" : "192.168.1.1", "port" : 8080},
       {"host" : "192.168.1.2", "port" : 8080},
       {"host" : "192.168.1.3", "port" : 8080}
    ]}